(2000002216,'The path of freedom has always been beset with tragedy, sire. We could not risk losing you. The Crusade could not have survived such a blow.',0,0,0,1,NULL),
(2000002217,'%s grimaces.',0,2,0,0,NULL),
(2000002218,'It should have been me that carried the blade to Northrend. The burden was mine to bear.',0,0,0,1,NULL),
(2000002219,'But you are right, Irulon. The price of our freedom will undoubtedly cost thousands more of their lives.',0,0,0,1,NULL),
